abstract: New data showed that Abbott Laboratories’ new drug-coated heart stent, Xience V, ouperformed the market leader in preventing coronary arteries from clogging again.
snippet: New data showed that Abbott Laboratories’ new drug-coated heart stent, Xience V, ouperformed the market leader in preventing coronary arteries from clogging again.
lead_paragraph: The data continues to be favorable for Abbott Laboratories’ new drug-coated heart stent, Xience V, which the company is hoping will win federal approval.

headline.main: Data Seen as Favorable for Abbott’s Proposed Heart Stent
